You’re correct 👍 — in Spring Batch 5 / Spring Boot 3, JobBuilderFactory and StepBuilderFactory are deprecated/removed.
Now we create JobBuilder and StepBuilder directly using JobRepository and PlatformTransactionManager.

Below is the updated Spring Batch 5 style implementation for your scenario.

⸻

1️⃣ Job Configuration (Spring Batch 5 Style)

@Configuration
@EnableBatchProcessing
public class BatchConfig {

    @Bean
    public Job csvImportJob(JobRepository jobRepository,
                            Step listFilesStep,
                            Step processFileStep,
                            Step moveFileStep) {

        return new JobBuilder("csvImportJob", jobRepository)
                .start(listFilesStep)
                .next(processFileStep)
                .next(moveFileStep)
                .build();
    }
}


